Key Improvements

Enhanced Condition Handling:

Now properly recognizes queries with = and != conditions

Normalizes conditions to [CONDITION] placeholder for better matching

Gives appropriate weight to conditional queries

Improved Pattern Matching:

Handles quoted values and numeric conditions

Better recognition of similar queries with different condition values

Self-Learning Weights:

Automatically generates weights from schema

Updates weights based on user feedback

Persists weights between sessions

Better Table Identification:

Gives bonus to tables likely to contain conditions

Maintains original matching logic for non-conditional queries
